data.description: Custom built brick ranch with extras.  Fenced rear yard, custom brick storage building, full length front porch, & full length rear screen porch, open air dining patio & custom brick paver patio area with masonry fire pit all on .58 acres with lush fescue lawn & surrounded by park like landscaping. Inside find 3 bedrooms, & 2.5 bathrooms on main level & huge bonus room over garage.  Custom features include 9' ceilings with tall vaults and trays, real oak hardwood floors, ornate moldings, fireplace with gas logs, nice light fixtures with many dimmers.  You'll also find plantation shutters on some windows. Extremely functional split bedroom floor plan that's very easy to live in with the important spaces exactly where they need to be.  Laundry room is large with cabinets, counter space, storage & windows.   New water heater in 2019, gas heat & air in 2018, electric stove in 2019. Awesome location: Carson High School District
